title: Laugh & Learn® Smart Stages™ Chair
description: It’s the best seat in the house for the toddler in your life! The Laugh & Learn Smart Stages Chair features Smart Stages technology, with learning content that changes as baby grows.  “Magic” ABC seat knows when baby sits, activating songs and phrases when baby stands. 50+ sing-along songs, tunes and phrases, with three levels of play. Ages 12 months & up.
